{
  "stem": "7683.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the group, in the Jewish, the one-- you see, I was Polish, and all my friends were involved in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I went with a Dutch girl and people what didn't speak Yiddish or Polish, they were considered be careful.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't talk to them because they might bubble and tell what's going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a big secret.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a small group only.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And mostly was it Polish Jews what they planned and they talk with Sasha, the group of his group.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the plan they told him, as I say, you cannot run away just like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Has to be organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he organized a plan how to run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was planned for everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a plan just a few run away or things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was planned for the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was not-- although there was secretive, but it was not to leave somebody normally, leave somebody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was planned the whole camp should go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the plan was we usually worked till 5 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that time is it already starts to get dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was in October.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was the plan was, an hour before we stopped working, the uprising will begin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, the uprising was made up of in each group, wherever we worked, there was about two, three Germans would supervise or chaperoned us, supervised us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in each group was assigned two, three people to do-- kill other these Germans in the group with the work and do it in a so way, so hidden that nobody knew what's going on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, for example, there-- as I said, we had the tailors and the shoemaker and the goldsmith.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
